Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个体防壁还挺厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 我们用不同波长来攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能同化吗
