Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:02.87,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}知晓了伤痕累累的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:07.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}那坚强而虚渺的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:14.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}随之而来的沉重负担
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:19.35,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}令其熟透落地 回归尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.19,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Follow me Follow you 即便痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:24.92,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Follow me Follow you 唯愿相通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.96,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}释放这沸腾热血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:35.39,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}战栗在冲突之中 从天而降的堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:40.64,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}可要过早地将早熟的果实 吞噬殆尽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:46.13,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}几度挣扎 总不忘仰问苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:49.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}确认你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:54.07,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}无意与人假装和气 徒增太多恸哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:59.33,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}混乱在纠葛之中 只为活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:05.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}即便如此 我们仍在追寻
