Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把力量都用来防御
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算机体没事 我们也撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核在保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则刚才那下就全军覆没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去 远见学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了Mk.Nicht
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无之子就这点能耐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体再生了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来注入妨碍其实体化的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽不能打倒它 但应该能阻止其行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 毁掉敌人的结晶核
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了恶魔型和阿撒谢尔型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拯救了被同化的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还令交战规定α撤回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底见证了多少奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒谢尔型消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌群开始散去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求各队救助伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里受损巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认各地情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁史彦 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你送来自己的孩子 原本守护自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑哥哥和总士哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会消失吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果继续使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天会被力量所同化的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是以自己的意志决定前来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了美羽你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 祈愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的敌人结晶核逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是星核的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寻找追踪需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再来 就到时再打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有系统 却传达了许多人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 请守护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…这有几万人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们来守护这所有人吗？
